Ukraine has become one of the famous destinations among Indian students who want to pursue their MBBS from abroad. Ukraine comprises several top-class Medical Colleges/Universities that provide MBBS, MD, and other degrees in medicine at reasonable fees. The students who complete their MBBS from MCI approved Medical Colleges in Ukraine are eligible to apply for a job in any part of the world.

The main benefit of studying MBBS in Ukraine is to make the students familiar with theoretical and practical knowledge in Medicine. The students are awarded the degree as MD Physician after completing MBBS in Ukraine. The degree is equivalent to MBBS in India as per the Medical Council of India (MCI).

Study MBBS in Ukraine from MCI approved University

Ukraine is one of the most preferable destinations for the students who want to study MBBS in abroad from MCI approved University because of the following reasons:

  • The medical universities of Ukraine are recognized by WHO, MCI, and the medical councils of many other counties.
  • The medium of instruction in Ukraine is English which makes it much easier for Indian students.
  • The cost of accommodation is low as compared to other countries. Travel to Ukraine is very economical.
  • MCI approved University provides high-quality facilities to the students.
  • Study MBBS in Ukraine from MCI approved University offers several opportunities to participate in the international exchange programs, conferences, and other scientific projects in several international universities.
  • Indian students who complete their MBBS from a Medical University of Ukraine can easily get a job in India and abroad as the MBBS degree obtained from a Ukraine University is recognized by MCI.
  • MCI approved University in Ukraine provides the best quality of education with good quality infrastructure facilities.
  • The students do not need to pay any donation and capitalization fee for getting admission to a medical college in Ukraine.
  • The students become eligible for working in government hospitals after study MBBS in Ukraine from MCI approved University

From the above description, the students must have got a clear idea about all the top MCI approved Medical Colleges in Ukraine to study MBBS. It enables students to make a decision that in which university they want to take admission. Moreover, all the universities/colleges in the above list are excellent places to study MBBS course.
